        <div class="meta">Guide</div>
        <h1>Construction Software Hidden Costs: The Real TCO</h1>
        <p>The subscription price you see in the pricing page is just the beginning. Here's the full cost of owning and operating construction software — and how to budget for it accurately.</p>
      </div>
